#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/versioned_docs/version-0.5.0/lua-api/re.md:3
msgid "Regular expression helpers are available under `ptool.re` and `p.re`."
msgstr "正则表达式辅助能力位于 `ptool.re` 和 `p.re` 下。"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/versioned_docs/version-0.5.0/lua-api/re.md:5
msgid "ptool.re.compile"
msgstr "ptool.re.compile"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/versioned_docs/version-0.5.0/lua-api/re.md:7
msgctxt "/Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/versioned_docs/version-0.5.0/lua-api/re.md:7"
msgid "`v0.1.0` - Introduced."
msgstr "`v0.1.0` - 引入。"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/versioned_docs/version-0.5.0/lua-api/re.md:9
msgid ""
"`ptool.re.compile(pattern[, opts])` compiles a regular expression and "
"returns a `Regex` object."
msgstr "`ptool.re.compile(pattern[, opts])` 编译正则表达式，并返回一个 `Regex` 对象。"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/versioned_docs/version-0.5.0/lua-api/re.md:12
msgid "`pattern` (string, required): The regex pattern."
msgstr "`pattern`（string，必填）：正则模式。"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/versioned_docs/version-0.5.0/lua-api/re.md:13
msgid "`opts` (table, optional): Compile options. Currently supported:"
msgstr "`opts`（table，可选）：编译选项。目前支持："

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/versioned_docs/version-0.5.0/lua-api/re.md:13
msgid ""
"`case_insensitive` (boolean, optional): Whether matching is case-"
"insensitive. Defaults to `false`."
msgstr "`case_insensitive`（boolean，可选）：是否大小写不敏感。默认值是 `false`。"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/versioned_docs/version-0.5.0/lua-api/re.md:17
